You will need to confirm your identity with PDS. This card is not accepted at all EU merchants that accept Mastercard.

Select a virtual Prepaid Mastercard, ready for use instantly after registering to PDS Website.

Use your account at some merchants where you see the Mastercard Acceptance Mark online or over the phone. Or, select a physical Prepaid Mastercard, to be mailed to you (handling fee of EUR 5.00 to be deducted from card balance).

The digital reward website provides balance information and transaction history to help you keep track of all your rewards.
